{
  "stem": "7777.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Like there come this guy Lahotka.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Yeah, and a couple days later it was again a new Judenrate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They just left the old Judenrate president.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the other one was taken with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this president-- they find out some other people and they make another committee, a Judenrate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they [INAUDIBLE] the people what they got left-- they worked by this-- by the bricks, what they make the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the Judenrate give for these people what they want to eat lunch.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The Judenrate have lunch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Friday, the 18 of September, is the guy-- is a guy from the police come, Lahotka, and he take-- and he took-- said he need 10 people for work.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They picked up 10 young people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We come over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- he ask, who is an engineer?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody answered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Later, he-- he on-- what the [NON-ENGLISH], the police was over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was not far from the woods.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wanted to clean up, to make a bright way to go to the woods.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We walk over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We cleaned up, all around, and make it-- this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "About 5 o'clock, we go for lunch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When it becomes lunch, is the-- going back from lunch, I see two trucks with the German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I-- maybe they're passing by.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We work till 5 o'clock. 5 o'clock, a police comes out with a gun, with ammunition, and he start to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was cleaned up over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was over there a woods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He gave out saws to cut the woods-- just to cut.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We cut the woods as it got dark.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It got dark, he took us where to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They put us in, in a basement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a little bit window open, over there in the basement.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we said, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
